snippet.textDisplay:
TALHA ANJUM VERSE WITH MEANING OF DIFFICULT WORDS:
Mile dard bohot, kabhi tu bhi mil
Dil mein rehti nahi, jaan ab tu hi dil
Aaj phir aayi na tu, intizaar raha mustaqil (constantly)
Taweel (long) hai gham ki shaam, kahaani muhabbat ki mukhtasir
Nazr-e-saani (re-check) karo zara si
Qadar karo meri kalla ki
Jaane wale chale jaate hain
Qismatain hi to qaabu main nahi aati
Chhaun mein dhoop ki tarah
Jism mein rooh (soul) ki tarah
Guzre dimaagh se yaad teri lagataar lahu (blood) ki tarah
Khaye jayen mujhe yeh dar o deewar kisi bhook ki tarah
Tere bina nahi ghar bhi ghar, akele mehsoos yeh kiya
Teri kami poori hui na, aaj bhi rahi aik dil mein khala (vaccuum)
Khizan (autumn) bhi aayi par vaqt aur dil ka baagh bhi raha na hara
Tera hi aitibaar baqi saari dunya pe bharosa nahi bana
Tu mujh mein dekhe insaan baaqi saari dunya ko dikhe bas kalla
Tu hai, main hun, aur gehri khamoshi
Ham donon hi nahin sunte jo kuchh bhi yeh kehti hogi
Gali hai dil ki tang ab tera us mein aana na ho
Dil ke mohalle mein ab tere mera jaana na ho
Tu hai, main hun, aur sirf faasle hain
Raabte munqata (disconnected) aur muntazir ham aapke hain
Raaz hi nahi raazdar hi kiya mangte ham
Khaamion (flaws) pe parde log kam hi yahan daalte hain
Ham sirhaane rakh ke khuwaab raatain jaagte hain
Ham tumhe tumse bohot behtar jaante hain
